results.snippet: On hand at the Johnson Space Center in Houston for the first full day of planning for the United States-Russian space flight scheduled for 1975, Alexei Leonov, the Soviet cosmonaut who was the first man to walk in space, was asked if he anticipated...
results.lead_paragraph: On hand at the Johnson Space Center in Houston for the first full day of planning for the United States-Russian space flight scheduled for 1975, Alexei Leonov, the Soviet cosmonaut who was the first man to walk in space, was asked if he anticipated any language problems on the joint mission.
